    "body": "Did you try this workaround?\r\nbefore calling any gRPC methods, just set the environment variables programmatically by `SetEnvironmentVariable(string variable, string value)`?\r\nhttps://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/library/z46c489x(v=vs.110).aspx\r\n\r\nIn addition to that, for filtering out some C-core logs in the C# layer, you can also use some stuff from https://github.com/grpc/grpc/tree/master/src/csharp/Grpc.Core/Logging (e.g. see `LogLeverFilterLogger`)."
